Package game.items

Interface SpecialScrap

All Known Implementing Classes:
Fruit, LargeFruit, MetalPipe, SmallFruit
public interface SpecialScrap

SpecialScrap Interface

The SpecialScrap interface represents the contractual obligation necessary for SpecialScrap classes to implement. This interface outlines methods needed by Items to determine whether an Item can be considered a SpecialScrap or not. This class has been instantiated for future implementation.
